{"TopicId":214507,"ForumId":198,"TopicTitle":"Nav Ball ist umgedreht","CreatedByName":"Grendor","CreatedById":227417,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-05T18:50:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Grendor","CreatedById":227417,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-05T18:50:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDer Nav Ball bzw. die gesamte Navigation ist spiegelverkehrt. Beim Start wird also nicht der Himmel angezeigt sondern die Erde.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDas ganze \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E System bugt auch komplett rum. St\u00E4ndiges gegensteuern das macht alles instabil.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003EThe Nav Ball or the entire navigation is mirrored.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003EAt the start, the sky is not displayed, but the earth.\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003EThe whole\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cabbr style=\u0022border-bottom:none;\u0022 title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Esystem also bugs around completely.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cfont style=\u0022vertical-align:inherit;\u0022\u003EConstant countermeasures make everything unstable.\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-05T23:24:30Z\u0022 title=\u002203/05/2023 11:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 5, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EPlease post in English when not using the International subforums.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dwing","CreatedById":226306,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-06T12:16:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have multiple crew modules, maybe one of them inverted for a lander? Try selecting the one in the right direction and select \u0022Control/Steer from here\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSchau mal ob du mehrere Kapseln hast, eventuell ist eine davon auf dem Kopf zum landen. W\u00E4hle dann die richtige aus, und dr\u00FCck auf \u0022Von hier steuern\u0022.\u00A0 Dann sollte es gehen. Das Problem hatte ich auch schon, dass \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E dann direkt nach dem Start die Rakete um 180\u00B0 gedreht und in den Boden gelenkt hat.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Grendor","CreatedById":227417,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T23:15:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, I didn\u0027t, but I reloaded the game and saw that the controls were set upside down for whatever reason.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}